     H            Y.
     FAKBPL07 IF  E           K        DISK
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@HIN1  5
     C                     PARM           P@HIN2  5
     C                     PARM           P@HIN3  2
     C                     PARM           P@BAN1  1
     C                     PARM           P@BAN2  2
     C                     PARM           P@BAN3  2
     C                     PARM           P@BAN4  1
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@BAN1  1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@BAN2  2
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@BAN3  2
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@BAN4  1
      *
     C                     MOVE P@HIN1    K@HIN1  5
     C                     MOVE P@HIN2    K@HIN2  5
     C                     MOVE P@HIN3    K@HIN3  2
      *
     C           AKBKEY    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@HIN1
     C                     KFLD           K@HIN2
     C                     KFLD           K@HIN3
      *
     C           AKBKEY    SETGTAKBPL07
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           AKBKEY    REDPEAKBPL07                  88
     C   88                LEAVE
     C           L1SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C                     ITER
     C                     END
      *
     C           *DATE     IFGE L1UKHZ
     C           *DATE     ANDLTL1STHZ
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ITER
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE L1TKR1    P@BAN1
     C                     MOVE L1TKR2    P@BAN2
     C                     MOVE L1TKR3    P@BAN3
     C                     MOVE L1TKR4    P@BAN4
     C                     LEAVE
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
